ZH: 我带了一大笔现金去购物。
EN: I took a large sum of cash to go shopping.

ZH: 这家商店只收现金。
EN: This store only accepts cash.

ZH: 我们不常用现金，都是用信用卡付账。
EN: We don't use cash often, we usually pay with credit cards.

ZH: 我在银行取了很多现金。
EN: I withdrew a lot of cash from the bank.

ZH: 你能否换一张100元的现金给我？
EN: Can you exchange a 100 yuan bill for me?

ZH: 他们只接受欧元现金付款。
EN: They only accept Euro cash payments.

ZH: 请用现金付账，不接受信用卡。
EN: Please pay with cash, credit cards are not accepted.

ZH: 确保你带够了现金去旅行。
EN: Make sure you bring enough cash when traveling.

ZH: 这家店只收美元现金。
EN: This store only accepts US dollar cash.

ZH: 我在街边花了所有的现金。
EN: I spent all my cash on the street.

ZH: 他突然用现金付了账。
EN: He suddenly paid the bill in cash.

ZH: 他带着大量的现金旅行。
EN: He travels with a large amount of cash.

ZH: 你可以选择现金或信用卡付款。
EN: You can choose to pay with cash or credit card.

ZH: 我没带现金，只能用信用卡付款。
EN: I didn't bring any cash, I can only pay with credit card.

ZH: 她从银行取了一些现金作为备用。
EN: She withdrew some cash from the bank as backup.

ZH: 他的钱包里总是装着很多现金。
EN: His wallet always contains a lot of cash.

ZH: 请记得把现金放进保险柜里。
EN: Remember to put the cash in the safe.

ZH: 我要去银行存现金。
EN: I need to go to the bank to deposit cash.

ZH: 请注意，现金易被盗。
EN: Please be aware that cash is easily stolen.

ZH: 他宁愿花现金也不用信用卡。
EN: He would rather spend cash than use a credit card.
